[size=24pt][b]HLT token[/b][/size]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/LPrhYah.png[/img]

[size=15pt]Ticker: [b]HLT[/b]
[b]1 HLT = 0.25 USD[/b]

In circulation, 1st January 2019 = [b]174,000,000[/b]
Total supply in 10 years = [b]1,000,000,000[/b]

[b]Zero pre-mine. All mine started on 5th July, 2018.  
Emission using Ethereum smart contract. Daily emission, declines by 0.1% per day[/b]

[b]40%[/b] of emission goes to HyperLoot MasterNode network
[b]30%[/b] goes to HyperLoot investment fund (to finance game dev and partnerships)
[b]30%[/b] goes to finance HyperLoot DAO, Estonian non-profit foundation
[/size]

[size=24pt][b]What is HLT token needed for?[/b][/size]

[size=18pt][b]Stacking[/b][/size]
[size=15pt]This is required in order to do digital assets emission and provide reserves that is used to guarantee asset quality[/size]

[size=18pt][b]Clearing[/b][/size]
[size=15pt]HLT reserves are used to riskless clearing  & settlement[/size]

[size=18pt][b]Liquidity[/b][/size]
[size=15pt]Integration of new liquidity providers requires reserves to fund smart contract relays[/size]

[size=18pt][b]MasterNodes[/b][/size]
[size=15pt]HLT is the only funding way to purchase master node tokens (HLTM)[/size]

[size=18pt][b]Exchange[/b][/size]
[size=15pt]If you don‚Äôt want to be charged trading fees, you will need to have HLT (think of it as Binance token, with 100% discount)[/size]

[size=18pt][b]Governance[/b][/size]
[size=15pt]HLT voting is the main governance mechanism for the DAO (i.e. create and upvote proposals).[/size]



[size=15pt]You can use them to create your in-game assets that retain value by staking and utilizing our tokenization and transaction protocol. Or buy items on our marketplace.  You may need that cool gun from that other guy. You can freely trade them to any available trading pair at any time.[/size]


